OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,FA Reverend in Lostwithiel says she's
OL,7,F'furious' Cornwall Council has ordered
OL,8,Fher church to remove a wooden
OL,9,Faccessibility ramp.
OL,11,FThe local authority says it's a
OL,12,F'nuisance' and has been causing an
OL,13,F'obstruction' in the road, but members
OL,14,Fof the church say to remove it without
OL,15,Fwithout any plans to drop the curb is
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory.
OL,18,FReverend Sheila Bawden says the old
OL,19,Fwooden ramp has been in place for 20
OL,20,For more years with no issues.
