OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,F"This ramp enables those who've got
OL,7,Fdisabilities to come up onto the curb
OL,8,Fto access their church. Not only that,
OL,9,Ffuneral directors need to get the
OL,10,Ftrolley over (the curb) to come in.
OL,11,FIt's there for a purpose."
OL,13,FShe goes on to say the ramp is on the
OL,14,Finside of double yellows so "nobody
OL,15,Fshould be parking there anyway."
