OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,FIn the letter Cornwall Council says it
OL,7,Fhas to act on issues that have been
OL,8,Fidentified as potentially hazardous
OL,9,Fand it has the power to remove any
OL,10,Fobjects from the highway which are
OL,11,Fcausing an obstruction or nuisance and
OL,12,Frecover any expenses incurred.
OL,14,FOne of those who rely on the ramp is
OL,15,Fcaptain of the bellringers Simon
OL,16,FBrewer who says "that's the only way I
OL,17,Fcan get in and out" of the church.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
