OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,F"(Cornwall Council) are more concerned
OL,7,Fwith a little piece of wood, three
OL,8,Ffoot by four inches, than all the
OL,9,Fpotholes we've through the town and
OL,10,Fthe drains.
OL,12,F"For the council to send a letter
OL,13,Flike, well, they want their heads
OL,14,Fseeing to."
OL,16,FReverend Bawden says the local
OL,17,Fauthority has communicated this issue
OL,18,Freally poorly.
