OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,FShe said: "I was shocked but also
OL,7,Ffurious because of the language of the
OL,8,Fletter too.
OL,10,F"It says here; Cornwall Council as
OL,11,FHighways Authority has a duty to
OL,12,Fensure the highway is kept free from
OL,13,Fobstructions/nuisances.
OL,15,F"You'd think there would be more
OL,16,Fimportant things for CORMAC to do."
OL,18,FSince sending the original letter
OL,19,Fdated 11th June, Cornwall Council has
OL,20,Fsince said it will not be taking any
OL,21,Fimmediate action.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
