OL,3,CReverend 'furious' after being told to
OL,4,Cremove church wheelchair ramp
OL,6,FIn a statement they say:
OL,8,F"Cornwall Council has a responsibility
OL,9,Fto the users of the highway and to act
OL,10,Fon issues that have been identified as
OL,11,Fpotentially hazardous."
OL,13,F"We will look at the options for how
OL,14,Fwe can support the Church to improve
OL,15,Faccess. In the meantime, while we will
OL,16,Fnot be taking any immediate action on
OL,17,Fthis matter, we have reminded the
OL,18,FChurch of their liabilities should any
OL,19,Faccidents occur relating to the
OL,20,Ftemporary ramp."
